{"tid":1622961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[研究策略] 打爛既店 應該搵人做個priority list?","createTime":"2019-10-04T17:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:00:46.000Z","uid":263103,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63cb7719ba58c34cc978c18b64f10ecc7b13adbb","tid":1622961,"uid":263103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:46:01.000Z","msg":"睇返今日打爛既店 好多都會比人搶野<br />\n當然一定會入晒我地數  亦當然大家未必會CARE <br />\n但長久咁樣會蝕卓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻擊既藍店, 可以主攻關左既藍色大財團食店. <br />\n裡面無咩值錢野, 但裝修費對比仍地每日收入既比例上, 蝕既會更多. <br />\n佢地最緊張D資產! 而且暴動係唔會有錢賠. <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以哩D店一被破壞後, 就好難再開返. 好似富臨果D咁. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦達到我地樂意見到既香港市容. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩D係夢中食飯時, 同幾個開食店朋友得出既睇法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有無其他睇法? 分享下. <br />\n<br />\n林鄭同政府識得LIST一個表 逐樣同我地推<br />\n我地都可以出一個表  逐個財團同佢地玩 要佢地逐間跪低! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時因為咁而求情既財團:<br />\n1. 褲臨<br />\n2. 美心<br />\n3. 麻雀館<br />\n4. 鳩品360"},{"pid":"dfd6c62c4b352bbcfaf9e8c3327d6e37e10b4275","tid":1622961,"uid":263103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:50:42.000Z","msg":"自己推唔到 手足幫手推一推"},{"pid":"87346003beeed60d9bf4cbccc2861761141a52a1","tid":1622961,"uid":263103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:51:07.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"1fad998ced655b402d26d27693ee